message.text:
📣 APPLICATION PERIOD EXTENDED‼️⏳

Hindi pa ba kumpleto ang requirements mo o hindi ka pa nakakapagpasa ng application? Worry no more—dahil may good news kami para sa’yo! 

Extended na ang ating application period! May dagdag na oras ka na para ayusin, tapusin, at siguraduhing maipasa ang lahat ng iyong kailangan. 📑

Huwag nang hintayin ang huling araw—gamitin ang mga oras na ito para makumpleto ang iyong application at maging bahagi ng kwentong bubuuin natin ngayong taon.

Kilalanin pa ang FEU IABF Student Council S.Y. 2025–2026 divisions dito: https://bit.ly/IABF_SC_Division_Description_and_Requirements

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
#ICYMI | Huling Biyahe ng Lakbay Piyu 2025! ✈️✨

Bawat sandali ay parang paglipad patungo sa bagong alaala. Mabilis man o mabagal, bawat tawa at kwento ay nag-iwan ng marka sa ating paglalakbay. 🌍✨

Sa huling dalawang araw ng saya, pagtuklas, at samahan lahat ay hindi malilimutan. 

Naging espesyal ang mga araw na ito dahil sa inyo, Tams! 😊

Photos by: Enzo Abello & Sharlene Rabusa
Edited by: Enzo Abello 

#TamHunt2025

message.text:
#ICYMI | Huling Biyahe ng Lakbay Piyu 2025! ✈️✨

Bawat sandali ay parang paglipad patungo sa bagong alaala. Mabilis man o mabagal, bawat tawa at kwento ay nag-iwan ng marka sa ating paglalakbay. 🌍✨

Sa huling dalawang araw ng saya, pagtuklas, at samahan lahat ay hindi malilimutan. 

Naging espesyal ang mga araw na ito dahil sa inyo, Tams! 😊

Photos by: Enzo Abello & Sharlene Rabusa
Edited by: Enzo Abello

message.text:
#ICYMI | Huling Biyahe ng Lakbay Piyu 2025! ✈️✨

Bawat sandali ay parang paglipad patungo sa bagong alaala. Mabilis man o mabagal, bawat tawa at kwento ay nag-iwan ng marka sa ating paglalakbay. 🌍✨

Sa huling dalawang araw ng saya, pagtuklas, at samahan lahat ay hindi malilimutan. 

Naging espesyal ang mga araw na ito dahil sa inyo, Tams! 😊

Photos by: Enzo Abello & Sharlene Rabusa
Edited by: Enzo Abello 

#TamHunt2025

Ka-Bio! still clueless what BioPHAGE does and how it came to life? Then, here’s something to digest:

𝗕𝗶𝗼𝗣𝗛𝗔𝗚𝗘, the Official Newsletter of the FEU Biological Science Society, was originally founded on 𝗔𝘂𝗴𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝟭𝟲, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟬. Throughout the years, it has been standing firm with its objective to create meaningful change through collaboration, 𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙞𝙫𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙩𝙤 𝙚𝙢𝙥𝙤𝙬𝙚𝙧 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙮𝙤𝙪𝙩𝙝’𝙨 𝙫𝙤𝙞𝙘𝙚 𝙗𝙮 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙘𝙤𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙣𝙪𝙤𝙪𝙨 𝙞𝙣𝙘𝙤𝙧𝙥𝙤𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙛 𝙨𝙘𝙞𝙚𝙣𝙘𝙚 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙟𝙤𝙪𝙧𝙣𝙖𝙡𝙞𝙨𝙢.

With its current battlecry, “𝗧𝗿𝗮𝗻𝘀𝗰𝗲𝗻𝗱𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗚𝗮𝗽 𝗼𝗳 𝗦𝗰𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗝𝗼𝘂𝗿𝗻𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘀𝗺” BioPHAGE now embodies a broader mission 𝙩𝙤 𝙗𝙧𝙞𝙙𝙜𝙚 𝙨𝙘𝙞𝙚𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙛𝙞𝙘 𝙞𝙣𝙦𝙪𝙞𝙧𝙮 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙟𝙤𝙪𝙧𝙣𝙖𝙡𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙞𝙘 𝙚𝙭𝙥𝙧𝙚𝙨𝙨𝙞𝙤𝙣 in the hopes of making science accessible, innovative, and impactful towards the community.

message.text:
𝐌𝐚𝐜𝐫𝐨𝐩𝐡𝐚𝐠𝐞? 𝐁𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐩𝐡𝐚𝐠𝐞? 𝐍𝐨, 𝐢𝐭’𝐬 𝐁𝐢𝐨𝐏𝐇𝐀𝐆𝐄 ✨

Ka-Bio! still clueless what BioPHAGE does and how it came to life? Then, here’s something to digest:

𝗕𝗶𝗼𝗣𝗛𝗔𝗚𝗘, the Official Newsletter of the FEU Biological Science Society, was originally founded on 𝗔𝘂𝗴𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝟭𝟲, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟬. Throughout the years, it has been standing firm with its objective to create meaningful change through collaboration, 𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙞𝙫𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙩𝙤 𝙚𝙢𝙥𝙤𝙬𝙚𝙧 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙮𝙤𝙪𝙩𝙝’𝙨 𝙫𝙤𝙞𝙘𝙚 𝙗𝙮 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙘𝙤𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙣𝙪𝙤𝙪𝙨 𝙞𝙣𝙘𝙤𝙧𝙥𝙤𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙛 𝙨𝙘𝙞𝙚𝙣𝙘𝙚 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙟𝙤𝙪𝙧𝙣𝙖𝙡𝙞𝙨𝙢.

With its current battlecry, “𝗧𝗿𝗮𝗻𝘀𝗰𝗲𝗻𝗱𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗚𝗮𝗽 𝗼𝗳 𝗦𝗰𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗝𝗼𝘂𝗿𝗻𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘀𝗺” BioPHAGE now embodies a broader mission 𝙩𝙤 𝙗𝙧𝙞𝙙𝙜𝙚 𝙨𝙘𝙞𝙚𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙛𝙞𝙘 𝙞𝙣𝙦𝙪𝙞𝙧𝙮 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙟𝙤𝙪𝙧𝙣𝙖𝙡𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙞𝙘 𝙚𝙭𝙥𝙧𝙚𝙨𝙨𝙞𝙤𝙣 in the hopes of making science accessible, innovative, and impactful towards the community.

#TranscendingTheGap
#FEUBioPHAGE
